title: End Your Fear of Public Speaking Quickly and Easily
description:
Description

This course covers what the RELIEF methods are and how to use it.It is taught through course lectures teaching energy healing treatments of Chakra balancing, Emotional Freedom Techniques, and the Blue Diamond method.  Benefits:  Speaking with ease and confidence anywhere in front of anyone.Learn a new method of eliminating your fear of public speaking!

In this course, you will work with:

    Meridians
    Chakras
    Biofield
    Breathing for grounding
    Unconscious beliefs
    Brain balancing
    EFT
    And much more!

Who is the target audience?

    Any adult or teen suffering from social anxiety or fear of public speaking.
    Not for strict behaviorists
    Managers who need to talk in front of employees
    Thought leaders who want to share their messages with more confidence
    Udemy instructors who want to teach better

Requirements

    Have an open mind
    Want to get over fears about speaking in public
